---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Socials from "../components/Socials.astro";
---

<Layout title="Mike's Day Out 2024 Music Festival - April 13 & 20">
	<main>
		<img
			class="poster-text"
			src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/mikechella.com/Mike's+Day+Out+Transparent.png"
			alt="transparent poster with text only for Mike's Day Out music festival in Los Angeles, California on April 13 & 20 from 8PM to 3AM"
		/>
		<Footer />
		<Socials />
		<div class="poster-text">
			<h1>Mike's House presents Mike's Day Out 2024</h1>
			<h2>Lineup</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>ketchup</li>
				<li>Abbylicious</li>
				<li>Shredy</li>
				<li>wrmbrw</li>
				<li>feelzlikestevo</li>
				<li>f.synthetic</li>
				<li>manamoves</li>
				<li>steven g</li>
				<li>Lonzo</li>
				<li>La Grand</li>
				<li>Kiinfolks</li>
				<li>LÃ¨o Ovalle</li>
				<li>Mikezilla</li>
				<li>super fake</li>
				<li>Juan Latino</li>
				<li>Hosted by: Patrick Cloud</li>
				<li>Food provided by: El Cocinegro</li>
			</ul>
			<p>Mike's Day Out takes the Mike's House experience you love and brings it outside! Mike's House is a live streamed show that features up and coming DJs providing the vibes for a house party. Watch as the party goes from small kickback to a rager where truly anything can happen.

				We're featuring 15 DJs across 2 weekends with genres ranging from House, Tech House, Minimal, Rap, Disco, Afrobeat, R&B, and Jungle/DnB.</p>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		color: white;
		font-size: 20px;
	}
	div.poster-text {
		visibility: hidden;
	}
	.poster-text {
		max-height: 96vh;
		margin: 0 auto;
		display: block;
		margin-top: -10px;
		margin-bottom: -35px;
	}
	@media (max-width: 590px) {
		.poster-text {
			max-width: 435px;
			width: 100%;
			max-height: 96vh;
			display: block;
			margin-bottom: -15px;
		}
	}
	.astro-a {
		position: absolute;
		top: -32px;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translatex(-50%);
		width: 220px;
		height: auto;
		z-index: -1;
	}
	h1 {
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
	}
	.text-gradient {
		background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-size: 400%;
		background-position: 0%;
	}
	.instructions {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-light), 25%);
		background: linear-gradient(
			rgba(var(--accent-dark), 66%),
			rgba(var(--accent-dark), 33%)
		);
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
	}
	.instructions code {
		font-size: 0.8em;
		font-weight: bold;
		background: rgba(var(--accent-light), 12%);
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
		border-radius: 4px;
		padding: 0.3em 0.4em;
	}
	.instructions strong {
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
	}
	.link-card-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(24ch, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		padding: 0;
	}
</style>
